<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh-CN">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>VibeCoding 群聊分析报告 (2025-06-26)</title>
    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/chart.js@4.4.2/dist/chart.umd.min.js"></script>
    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/mermaid@10.9.0/dist/mermaid.min.js"></script>
    <style>
        :root {
            --bg-main: #FFFBF5;
            --bg-card: #FFFFFF;
            --bg-alt: #FFF7ED;
            --text-primary: #44403C;
            --text-secondary: #78716C;
            --accent-primary: #F97316;
            --accent-secondary: #EA580C;
            --border-color: #FDE68A;
            --shadow-color: rgba(217, 119, 6, 0.1);
            --chat-bubble-1: #FEF3C7;
            --chat-bubble-2: #FFE4E6;
            --tag-bg: #FFEDD5;
            --tag-text: #9A3412;
        }

        @import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Noto+Sans+SC:wght@300;400;500;700&display=swap');

        body {
            font-family: 'Noto Sans SC', -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", Roboto, "Helvetica Neue", Arial, sans-serif;
            background-color: var(--bg-main);
            color: var(--text-primary);
            margin: 0;
            padding: 2rem 1rem;
            line-height: 1.7;
        }

        .container {
            max-width: 1400px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 0 1rem;
        }

        header {
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 3rem;
        }

        header h1 {
            font-size: 2.5rem;
            font-weight: 700;
            color: var(--accent-secondary);
            margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
        }

        header p {
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            color: var(--text-secondary);
        }

        .bento-grid {
            display: grid;
            gap: 1.5rem;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(12, 1fr);
            grid-auto-rows: auto;
        }

        .card {
            background-color: var(--bg-card);
            border-radius: 1.5rem;
            padding: 1.5rem 2rem;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 15px var(--shadow-color);
            border: 1px solid var(--border-color);
            transition: all 0.3s ease-in-out;
            overflow: hidden;
        }

        .card:hover {
            transform: translateY(-5px);
            box-shadow: 0 10px 25px var(--shadow-color);
        }

        .card-header {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 0.75rem;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
            padding-bottom: 0.75rem;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #f1f1f1;
        }

        .card-header .icon {
            font-size: 1.5rem;
            color: var(--accent-primary);
            width: 40px;
            height: 40px;
            background-color: var(--bg-alt);
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            border-radius: 50%;
        }

        .card-header h2 {
            font-size: 1.4rem;
            font-weight: 600;
            margin: 0;
            color: var(--text-primary);
        }

        .overview-card { grid-column: span 12; }
        .activity-card { grid-column: span 12; grid-row: span 2; }
        .theme-card { grid-column: span 12; }
        .concept-map-card { grid-column: span 12; }
        .quotes-card { grid-column: span 12; }
        .tools-card { grid-column: span 12; }

        .overview-stats {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-around;
            align-items: center;
            text-align: center;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            padding: 1rem 0;
        }

        .stat {
            flex: 1;
            min-width: 150px;
            padding: 1rem;
        }

        .stat .value {
            font-size: 2.5rem;
            font-weight: 700;
            color: var(--accent-secondary);
        }

        .stat .label {
            font-size: 0.9rem;
            color: var(--text-secondary);
            margin-top: 0.25rem;
        }

        .theme-container {
            display: grid;
            gap: 1.5rem;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));
        }

        .theme-item {
            background-color: var(--bg-alt);
            border-radius: 1rem;
            padding: 1.5rem;
            border: 1px solid var(--border-color);
        }

        .theme-item h3 {
            font-size: 1.2rem;
            color: var(--accent-secondary);
            margin-top: 0;
            margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
        }

        .theme-item p {
            font-size: 0.95rem;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
            color: var(--text-secondary);
        }

        .chat-snippet {
            font-size: 0.9rem;
            background-color: var(--bg-card);
            border-radius: 0.75rem;
            padding: 0.75rem 1rem;
            margin-top: 0.5rem;
            position: relative;
        }

        .chat-snippet strong {
            color: var(--accent-primary);
        }

        .chat-snippet::before {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            left: -8px;
            top: 12px;
            width: 0;
            height: 0;
            border-top: 8px solid transparent;
            border-bottom: 8px solid transparent;
            border-right: 8px solid var(--bg-card);
        }

        .quotes-grid {
            display: grid;
            gap: 1.5rem;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(320px, 1fr));
        }

        .quote-item {
            background-color: var(--chat-bubble-1);
            border-left: 5px solid var(--accent-primary);
            padding: 1.5rem;
            border-radius: 0.5rem 1rem 1rem 0.5rem;
        }

        .quote-item blockquote {
            margin: 0;
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            font-style: italic;
            font-weight: 500;
            color: var(--text-primary);
        }

        .quote-item .author {
            text-align: right;
            margin-top: 1rem;
            font-size: 0.9rem;
            color: var(--text-secondary);
        }

        .quote-item .author strong {
            color: var(--text-primary);
        }

        .tools-list {
            list-style: none;
            padding: 0;
            display: flex;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            gap: 0.75rem;
        }

        .tools-list li {
            background-color: var(--tag-bg);
            color: var(--tag-text);
            padding: 0.5rem 1rem;
            border-radius: 999px;
            font-weight: 500;
            font-size: 0.9rem;
        }

        /* Mermaid Diagram Styles */
        .mermaid {
            text-align: center;
            background-color: var(--bg-alt);
            padding: 1rem;
            border-radius: 1rem;
        }

        /* Responsive Design */
        @media (min-width: 768px) {
            .overview-card { grid-column: span 12; }
            .activity-card { grid-column: span 7; grid-row: span 2; }
            .tools-card { grid-column: span 5; grid-row: span 1; }
            .quotes-card { grid-column: span 5; grid-row: span 1; }
            .theme-card { grid-column: span 12; }
            .concept-map-card { grid-column: span 12; }
        }

        @media (min-width: 1200px) {
            .overview-card { grid-column: span 5; }
            .activity-card { grid-column: span 7; }
            .theme-card { grid-column: span 6; grid-row: span 2; }
            .concept-map-card { grid-column: span 6; grid-row: span 2; }
            .quotes-card { grid-column: span 12; }
            .tools-card { display: none; } /* Hide for a cleaner layout on large screens, or adjust */
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <header>
            <h1>VibeCoding 商业化和人类发展</h1>
            <p>单日群聊数据洞察报告: 2025年06月26日</p>
        </header>

        <main class="bento-grid">
            <section class="card overview-card">
                <div class="card-header">
                    <span class="icon">📊</span>
                    <h2>报告概览</h2>
                </div>
                <div class="overview-stats">
                    <div class="stat">
                        <div class="value">189</div>
                        <div class="label">消息总数</div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="stat">
                        <div class="value">174</div>
                        <div class="label">有效文本消息</div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="stat">
                        <div class="value">21</div>
                        <div class="label">活跃用户数</div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="stat">
                        <div class="value">2</div>
                        <div class="label">讨论高峰期</div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </section>

            <section class="card activity-card">
                <div class="card-header">
                    <span class="icon">📈</span>
                    <h2>全天讨论热度趋势</h2>
                </div>
                <canvas id="activityChart"></canvas>
            </section>

            <section class="card quotes-card">
                <div class="card-header">
                    <span class="icon">💬</span>
                    <h2>金句闪耀时刻</h2>
                </div>
                <div class="quotes-grid">
                    <div class="quote-item">
                        <blockquote>“你们程序员就喜欢折腾文具”</blockquote>
                        <p class="author">- <strong>谭嘉荣🔆Jaron</strong></p>
                    </div>
