                        <p class="author">- <strong>郭昊天</strong></p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="quote-item">
                        <blockquote>“天下苦微信久矣”</blockquote>
                        <p class="author">- <strong>兰天游</strong></p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="quote-item">
                        <blockquote>“我们通过Claude Code深度逆向工程成功破解了...所有系统提示词和架构设计。”</blockquote>
                        <p class="author">- <strong>Xlu shareAI</strong></p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </section>

            <section class="card tools-card">
                <div class="card-header">
                    <span class="icon">🛠️</span>
                    <h2>提及的工具与资源</h2>
